imdb.plot outline: "Unscripted Conversations" is a podcast series that will feature award winning filmmaker Antoine Allen and award winning actor/producer Lester Greene. They will discuss certain topics within the Industry, bringing two different perspectives to the conversation. Antoine specializes in business/marketing, and Lester brings hands-on acting experience from being in those audition rooms and being told, "No." The whole purpose of this series is to show creatives how to create their own opportunities by saying "Yes" to themselves. In this business, it's so hard to find like-minded people who make you feel safe and at home. Let "Unscripted Conversations" be a place of refuge and honest dialogue.
